  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">Overview</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        SensorUp is an IoT technology company at the forefront of sensor data innovation. As a leader in the Internet of Things space, they needed a strategic digital marketing partner to build their brand awareness and generate qualified leads among diverse audiences, from enterprise decision-makers to government agencies and technology partners.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">The Challenge</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        Communicating complex technology to diverse audiences is one of the most difficult challenges in B2B marketing. SensorUp's IoT platform offered powerful capabilities, but translating technical features into compelling value propositions for non-technical decision-makers required a nuanced marketing approach. The brand needed to build credibility and trust while making the technology feel accessible and relevant.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        We formed a strategic digital marketing partnership with SensorUp, developing a multi-channel approach that translated complex IoT technology into clear, compelling narratives. Our strategy included targeted content marketing, thought leadership positioning, and digital campaigns designed to reach key decision-makers across enterprise, government, and technology sectors. We focused on demonstrating real-world applications and measurable outcomes to build trust with potential clients.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">Results</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        The strategic digital marketing partnership delivered significant improvements in brand awareness and lead generation for SensorUp. The simplified messaging and targeted campaigns resonated with diverse audiences, helping SensorUp establish itself as a trusted name in the IoT space. The ongoing partnership continues to drive qualified leads and strengthen their market position across multiple sectors.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

